spec_data.Name: texlive-termlist
spec_data.Description:
The termlist package provides environments to indent and label
any kind of terms with a continuous number. Candidate terms may
appear inside an equation or eqnarray environment.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 07:44:04 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Label any kind of term with a continuous counter
